[['FinanceProductSearch.find_innovations', {'name': 'FinanceProductSearch.find_innovations', 'description': 'This function searches for innovative finance products based on time period and category.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'time_period', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The time period to search within, e.g., past_year, last_quarter.'}, {'name': 'category', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The category of finance products, e.g., consumer_finance, corporate_finance.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'innovations', 'description': 'A list of up to three innovative products, each with an ID, name, and provider.'}]}], ['FinanceProductSearch.get_product_details', {'name': 'FinanceProductSearch.get_product_details', 'description': 'This function retrieves detailed information about a specific finance product given its date and company.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'date', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The date when the product was launched.'}, {'name': 'company', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The name of the company that launched the product.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'details', 'description': 'Detailed information about the product, including features, terms, and conditions.'}]}], ['FinanceProductSearch.get_market_feedback', {'name': 'FinanceProductSearch.get_market_feedback', 'description': 'This function retrieves market feedback about a specific finance product given its ID.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'product_id', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The ID of the finance product.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'feedback', 'description': 'Market feedback about the product, including customer reviews and ratings.'}]}], ['FinanceProductSearch.get_innovation_strategy', {'name': 'FinanceProductSearch.get_innovation_strategy', 'description': 'This function retrieves the innovation strategy of a specific finance company given its name.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'company_name', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The name of the finance company.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'strategy', 'description': 'The innovation strategy of the company, including future plans and development suggestions.'}]}]]
请生成一个解决用户问题的计划，计划应该是一个行为列表，每个行为的格式如下:

[{
    // 动作的ID
    "id": number;
    // 动作要调用的API名称
    "name": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "args": "str(Record<string, any>)";
}, ...
]

你可以在计划中想象参数的值，这些指令将按顺序执行。
例如，如果你想调用 `FinanceProductSearch.find_innovations` 并传入 `time_period` 和 `category`，你可以写下面的计划:

[{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "FinanceProductSearch.find_innovations",
    "args": "{'time_period': 'past_year', 'category': 'consumer_finance'}",
}, ...
]

这些参数将在执行时被替换为真实的值。请注意，参数应该是一个字符串，而不是一个字典。
请在字典的参数中使用 ''，在其他地方使用 ""，不要打印值为 None 或 null 的参数。

你应该只生成一个 JSON 格式的计划列表。列表应该是完整的计划列表，不要有 `...`。
不要生成任何解释 JSON 的文本。

